rows.label: bf07530100_0030
rows.name:
Ah, you missed the highlight.
We already have everything we need from her.

rows.label: bf07530100_0040
rows.name: Shin! What did you do to her?

rows.label: bf07530100_0060
rows.name:
I'm just trying to get back what was stolen
from me five centuries ago.

rows.label: bf07530100_0080
rows.name:
Hah! You didn't think you could put me down
that easily, did you?

rows.label: bf07530100_0088
rows.name: I can't believe you fell for it.

rows.label: bf07530100_0100
rows.name:
She betrayed herself as an Holy Grail, forming
a bond with a piece of human trash.

rows.label: bf07530100_0110
rows.name:
She tried so pathetically hard to hold
on to her memories of you.

rows.label: bf07530100_0120
rows.name: But in the end, I got them all.

rows.label: bf07530100_0140
rows.name: She put up a brave little fight.

rows.label: bf07530100_0150
rows.name:
"Please don't steal my memories!"
Cute stuff like that.

rows.label: bf07530100_0160
rows.name:
Sorry, boy.
You came to this desolate place for nothing.

rows.label: bf07530100_0170
rows.name: Do you really want this useless husk?

rows.label: bf07530100_0200
rows.name: We made it this far, but...

rows.label: bf07530100_0270
rows.name:
What's this?
I thought you'd start bawling and charge at me.

rows.label: bf07530100_0315
rows.name: I didn't understand Homura and Hikari's feelings.

rows.label: bf07530100_0320
rows.name:
Though we were destined to follow different paths,
I tried to walk together.

rows.label: bf07530100_0330
rows.name: I walked in the shadow of the Holy Grail's light.

rows.label: bf07530100_0360
rows.name: So, I might be stupid...but I've made a decision.

rows.label: bf07530100_0380
rows.name: You've come all this way, I'll hear you out.

rows.label: bf07530100_0400
rows.name:
I'll crush you into oblivion,
and take Homura and Hikari to Eden!

rows.label: bf07530100_0410
rows.name:
Hah! Crush us?
Me and Shin? You couldn't take Shin on your own!

rows.label: bf07530100_0420
rows.name:
And on top of that, I've regained control
of all my Holy Grail powers!

rows.label: bf07530100_0460
rows.name:
That thing is just a used-up shell.
You can't rely on it to save you, boy.

rows.label: bf07530100_0480
rows.name: And I understand what I have to do to make it happen!

rows.label: bf07530100_0490
rows.name: What it means to be Driver and Blade!

rows.label: bf07530100_0510
rows.name: Everyone, stand with me one more time!

rows.label: bf07530100_0520
rows.name: Let's get Homura back, and go to Eden!
